This is how to solve of N:
   Remember that result is ""
   Remember that n is N
   Do this 1000 times:
      When n is at most 1, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
      Remember that r is remainder of n and 3
      Add result to tostring of r
      Remember that n is quotient of n and 3
   End do
   The answer is reverse of result
